name: The Goodest Tezonaut
description:
With a face like that, how could we refuse Tez's pleas for space flight?! "If greasy ol Bezo's can do it, so can I", he yips, wagging his tail as he loads up into the specially designed crypto-rocket.
"Screw the Moon, this dogs goin to Pluto!", he barks from the window as he blast off.

Godspeed, Tez.
